snippet.title: Critter Cove: Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Critter Cove is launching into Steam Early Access on September 10th, 2024!

Critter Cove is an open world life simulator with a focus on exploration, crafting and rebuilding an island community in the colorful post apocalypse.

It's just the start of our adventure, so join us in Discord and, if you haven't yet, wishlist us on Steam!

🎮 https://store.steampowered.com/app/1631470/Critter_Cove/
🗨️ https://discord.com/invite/QtUafGf

PS - If you can't wait until September, the demo is available now on Steam, and saves in the demo will carry straight over into the main game!
